00:00:01.580 --> 00:00:06.719
Faust handling of records is one of the most fun parts of using the framework.

00:00:06.719 --> 00:00:10.019
As you've seen, you can define a model once and use it for

00:00:10.019 --> 00:00:14.564
both serialization and deserialization, and type validation.

00:00:14.564 --> 00:00:18.419
